8552FeedbackSlot BytecodeGenerator::GetCachedLoadGlobalICSlot(
8553 TypeofMode typeof_mode, Variable* variable) {
8554 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind slot_kind =
8555 typeof_mode == TypeofMode::kInside
8556 ? FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kLoadGlobalInsideTypeof
8557 : FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kLoadGlobalNotInsideTypeof;
8558 FeedbackSlot slot(feedback_slot_cache()->Get(slot_kind, variable));
8559 if (!slot.IsInvalid()) {
8560 return slot;
8561 }
8562 slot = feedback_spec()->AddLoadGlobalICSlot(typeof_mode);
8563 feedback_slot_cache()->Put(slot_kind, variable, feedback_index(slot));
8564 return slot;
8565}

8567FeedbackSlot BytecodeGenerator::GetCachedStoreGlobalICSlot(
8568 LanguageMode language_mode, Variable* variable) {
8569 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind slot_kind =
8570 is_strict(language_mode)
8571 ? FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kStoreGlobalStrict
8572 : FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kStoreGlobalSloppy;
8573 FeedbackSlot slot(feedback_slot_cache()->Get(slot_kind, variable));
8574 if (!slot.IsInvalid()) {
8575 return slot;
8576 }
8577 slot = feedback_spec()->AddStoreGlobalICSlot(language_mode);
8578 feedback_slot_cache()->Put(slot_kind, variable, feedback_index(slot));
8579 return slot;
8580}
8581
8582FeedbackSlot BytecodeGenerator::GetCachedLoadICSlot(const Expression* expr,
8583 const AstRawString* name) {
8584 DCHECK(!expr->IsSuperPropertyReference());
8585 if (!v8_flags.ignition_share_named_property_feedback) {
8586 return feedback_spec()->AddLoadICSlot();
8587 }
8588 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind slot_kind =
8589 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kLoadProperty;
8590 if (!expr->IsVariableProxy()) {
8591 return feedback_spec()->AddLoadICSlot();
8592 }
8593 const VariableProxy* proxy = expr->AsVariableProxy();
8594 FeedbackSlot slot(
8595 feedback_slot_cache()->Get(slot_kind, proxy->var()->index(), name));
8596 if (!slot.IsInvalid()) {
8597 return slot;
8598 }
8599 slot = feedback_spec()->AddLoadICSlot();
8600 feedback_slot_cache()->Put(slot_kind, proxy->var()->index(), name,
8601 feedback_index(slot));
8602 return slot;
8603}
8604
8605FeedbackSlot BytecodeGenerator::GetCachedLoadSuperICSlot(
8606 const AstRawString* name) {
8607 if (!v8_flags.ignition_share_named_property_feedback) {
8608 return feedback_spec()->AddLoadICSlot();
8609 }
8610 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind slot_kind =
8611 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kLoadSuperProperty;
8612
8613 FeedbackSlot slot(feedback_slot_cache()->Get(slot_kind, name));
8614 if (!slot.IsInvalid()) {
8615 return slot;
8616 }
8617 slot = feedback_spec()->AddLoadICSlot();
8618 feedback_slot_cache()->Put(slot_kind, name, feedback_index(slot));
8619 return slot;
8620}
8621
8622FeedbackSlot BytecodeGenerator::GetCachedStoreICSlot(const Expression* expr,
8623 const AstRawString* name) {
8624 if (!v8_flags.ignition_share_named_property_feedback) {
8625 return feedback_spec()->AddStoreICSlot(language_mode());
8626 }
8627 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind slot_kind =
8628 is_strict(language_mode()) ? FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kSetNamedStrict
8629 : FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kSetNamedSloppy;
8630 if (!expr->IsVariableProxy()) {
8631 return feedback_spec()->AddStoreICSlot(language_mode());
8632 }
8633 const VariableProxy* proxy = expr->AsVariableProxy();
8634 FeedbackSlot slot(
8635 feedback_slot_cache()->Get(slot_kind, proxy->var()->index(), name));
8636 if (!slot.IsInvalid()) {
8637 return slot;
8638 }
8639 slot = feedback_spec()->AddStoreICSlot(language_mode());
8640 feedback_slot_cache()->Put(slot_kind, proxy->var()->index(), name,
8641 feedback_index(slot));
8642 return slot;
8643}
8644
8645int BytecodeGenerator::GetCachedCreateClosureSlot(FunctionLiteral* literal) {
8646 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind slot_kind =
8647 FeedbackSlotCache::SlotKind::kClosureFeedbackCell;
8648 int index = feedback_slot_cache()->Get(slot_kind, literal);
8649 if (index != -1) {
8650 return index;
8651 }
8652 index = feedback_spec()->AddCreateClosureParameterCount(
8653 JSParameterCount(literal->parameter_count()));
8654 feedback_slot_cache()->Put(slot_kind, literal, index);
8655 return index;
8656}
